pkgtools: pkgtools (Tukaani's Slackware compatible package maintenance system)
pkgtools:
pkgtools: pkgtools contains various utilities for managing Tukaani and
pkgtools: Slackware packages, such as 'installpkg', 'removepkg', upgradepkg',
pkgtools: 'makepkg', 'viewpkg' and 'explodepkg'. Also included are 'pkgtool',
pkgtools: which is a powerful menu-based program for managing packages,
pkgtools: 'makerepo' for creating package repositories for pkgtool, 'config-xwm'
pkgtools: for selecting X11 window manager, and a few other scripts. This
pkgtools: package includes 'dialog' and 'tar-1.13-pkgtools' binaries.
pkgtools:
pkgtools: http://tukaani.org/pkgtools/
